cscie97.asn1.knowledge.engine

Class KnowledgeGraph

  • java.lang.Object
    • cscie97.asn1.knowledge.engine.KnowledgeGraph

  • public class KnowledgeGraph
extends java.lang.Object
    The KnowledgeGraph class manages nodes, predicates, triples and query map. It manages node and predicate objects such that their instances are created only if corresponding identifiers are unique. Triple contains the references to node and predicate instances. Generates all of the eight permutations of a triple object. Stores each permutation in query map and maps it to the corresponding triple objects. This data structure forms the basis of a query in N_Triple format.
    Author:
    Siddharth Singh
